						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year <hi rend="italic">Siddhārthi, Vaikāśi</hi>, 13.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is in characters of the 16-17th century A.D. And it records the grant of ten <hi rend="italic">vēli</hi> of land for the sacred bath of the god, Koḻundīśura-svāmi at Koṭṭūr, by Raghunātha-Nāyakka. At the end it is stated that it is a charity of Seṇayakavalli Ammaṉ.</p>						

